<li>HNoMS <i>Thor Heyerdahl</i>, a frigate of the Norwegian Navys <a href="/wiki/Fridtjof_Nansen_class_frigate" title="Fridtjof Nansen class frigate">Fridtjof Nansen class frigates</a> named after him</li>
<li><i>Thor Heyerdahl</i>, a refurbished schooner, used for youth work and owned by a former member of the Tigris expedition <a href="http://www.thor-heyerdahl.de/" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.thor-heyerdahl.de/" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
